# Vibe Coding (Docs/)

1. **Skill:** `.cursor/skills/vibe-coding-workflow/SKILL.md`
2. **Doc boundaries:** `.cursor/rules/docs-roadmap-arch-sync.mdc` (canonical — no duplicate maps)
3. **Hygiene:** Active-Plan = `[ ]` only; done → Archived-Plan; one **WIP** Plan+Progress pair at Docs root (roadmap plans without Progress are OK — see sync rule)
4. **`@`:** WIP Plan + one Active-Plan P section; Architecture for policy only
5. **Close:** build/smoke or documented N/A; deviation protocol in skill
